PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FThe United Arab Emirates has said it
OL,7,Fis leaving Opec ` a cartel of oil-
OL,8,Fproducing countries that seeks to
OL,9,Fcontrol supplies and prices within the
OL,10,Fmarket.
OL,12,FIt announced the decision, via the
OL,13,Fstate-run WAM news agency, which will
OL,14,Fbe effective from May 1, after six
OL,15,Fdecades of membership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,F"This decision follows a comprehensive
OL,7,Freview of the UAE's production policy
OL,8,Fand its current and future capacity
OL,9,Fand is based on our national interest
OL,10,Fand our commitment to contributing
OL,11,Feffectively to meeting the market's
OL,12,Fpressing needs," the country said in a
OL,13,Fstatement.
OL,15,FThe UAE had been a longtime member of
OL,16,FOpec, first through its emirate of Abu
OL,17,FDhabi in 1967 and later when the UAE
OL,18,Fbecame its own country in 1971.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FIts departure will leave the oil
OL,7,Fcartel with 11 member countries,
OL,8,Fincluding Saudi Arabia, Iran and Iraq.
OL,10,FThe decision to leave Opec, and its
OL,11,Fwider Opec+ group, had been rumoured
OL,12,Ffor some time as the Emirates chafed
OL,13,Funder production restrictions and had
OL,14,Fincreasingly frosty relations with
OL,15,Fneighbouring Saudi Arabia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FIt comes as the UAE increasingly tries
OL,7,Fto leverage its own foreign policy in
OL,8,Fthe Middle East that has contradicted
OL,9,Fsome positions of Riyadh over time `
OL,10,Fparticularly as Saudi Arabia began to
OL,11,Fdirectly challenge the Emirates in
OL,12,Ftrying to draw foreign investments as
OL,13,Fthe kingdom opened up under Crown
OL,14,FPrince Mohammed bin Salman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,F"This decision reflects the UAE's long-
OL,7,Fterm strategic and economic vision and
OL,8,Fevolving energy profile, including
OL,9,Faccelerated investment in domestic
OL,10,Fenergy production, and reinforces its
OL,11,Fcommitment to a responsible, reliable,
OL,12,Fand forward-looking role in global
OL,13,Fenergy markets," the UAE said.
OL,15,F"Following its exit, the UAE will
OL,16,Fcontinue to act responsibly, bringing
OL,17,Fadditional production to market in a
OL,18,Fgradual and measured manner, aligned
OL,19,Fwith demand and market conditions,"
OL,20,Fthe country added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
