PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FWhat is Opec?
OL,8,FThe Organisation of the Petroleum
OL,9,FExporting Countries (OPEC) is a
OL,10,Fpermanent, intergovernmental
OL,11,Forganisation, created at the Baghdad
OL,12,FConference in September 1960, by Iran,
OL,13,FIraq, Kuwait, Saudi Arabia and
OL,14,FVenezuela.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
