PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FIt says its objective is to coordinate
OL,7,Fand unify petroleum policies among
OL,8,Fmember countries "in order to secure
OL,9,Ffair and stable prices for petroleum
OL,10,Fproducers; an efficient, economic and
OL,11,Fregular supply of petroleum to
OL,12,Fconsuming nations; and a fair return
OL,13,Fon capital to those investing in the
OL,14,Findustry".
OL,16,FOther countries have left and rejoined
OL,17,Fover the decades, but here is a list
OL,18,Fof current members:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
