PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FSaudi Arabia has long been considered
OL,7,Fa heavyweight of Opec, which is based
OL,8,Fin Vienna, and has seen some of its
OL,9,Fmarket power wane as the United States
OL,10,Fincreased its production of crude oil
OL,11,Fin recent years.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
