FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FOpec losing a member could be a win
OL,7,Ffor the administration of Donald
OL,8,FTrump, who during his first term in
OL,9,Foffice accused the group of "ripping
OL,10,Foff the rest of the world" by
OL,11,Finflating oil prices.
OL,13,FSaudi Arabia and the UAE increasingly
OL,14,Fhave competed over economic issues and
OL,15,Fregional politics, particularly in the
OL,16,FRed Sea area.
OL,18,FThe two countries had joined in
OL,19,Ftogether in a coalition to fight
OL,20,Fagainst Yemen's Iran-backed Houthi
OL,21,Frebels in 2015.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777449958
OL,3,CUnited Arab Emirates to leave OPEC
OL,4,Ccartel of oil producers
OL,6,FHowever, that coalition broke down
OL,7,Finto recriminations in late December,
OL,8,Fwhen Saudi Arabia bombed what it
OL,9,Fdescribed as a weapons shipment bound
OL,10,Ffor Yemeni separatists backed by the
OL,11,FUAE.
OL,13,FSaudi broadcasters, long based in
OL,14,FDubai, the economic hub of the UAE,
OL,15,Fhave pulled back to the kingdom in
OL,16,Frecent months as tensions rose.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
